headline: Morgan Stanley Investment Management Hits Hard Cap with Third Co-Investment Fund
summary: NEW YORK, April 14, 2025--Morgan Stanley Investment Management (MSIM), announced today the final close of North Haven Private Equity Co-Investment Opportunities Fund III LP (PECO III) oversubscribed at its hard cap with approximately $2.3 billion in total commitments. PECO III offers private equity exposure through co-investments alongside best-in-class buyout managers operating primarily in the lower middle market.
